Tori Black (born Michelle Chapman; August 26, 1988) is an American pornographic actress. She entered the adult film industry in 2007, and has since appeared in over 200 movies. In 2010, Black was named by "Loaded" magazine as the most facially attractive female performer in the industry. In 2011, lifestyle magazine Complex placed her top in their list "The Top 100 Hottest Porn Stars Right Now".
Career.
She was the "Penthouse" Pet of the Month for December 2008.
Black appeared in her first anal sex scene in the 2009 movie "Interactive Sex with Tori Black", with her first non-POV anal taking place in "Tori Black Is Pretty Filthy", also 2009. She partook in her first DP scene in the 2010 sequel, "Tori Black is Pretty Filthy 2".
Black is the first person in history to win two AVN Female Performer of the Year Award, winning back-to-back years in 2010 & 2011. In 2010, she was named by "Maxim" as one of the 12 top female stars in porn and in 2011 was named by CNBC as one of the 12 most popular stars in porn. CNBC noted her role as Catwoman in Vivid Entertainment's "", as well as her 2010 wins and 2011 nominations as Female Performer of the Year by both the AVN and XBIZ Award.
Personal life.
